(4, 4, '工建通商户入驻协议', '<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通商户入驻协议</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议由同意并承诺遵守本协议规定使用工建通服务的法律实体</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">下称</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">“</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">”</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">“</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">甲方</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">”)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">、黑龙江特讯科技有限责任公司</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">下称</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">“</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">”)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">共同缔结，本协议具有合同效力。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议中协议双方合称协议方。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一．协议内容及生效：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议内容包括协议正文及所有工建通平台已经发布的或将来可能发布的各类规则。所有规则为协议不可分割的一部分，与协议正文具有同等法律效力。工建通将就工建通平台服务制定特别规则</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">下称</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">“</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">特别规则</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">”)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">，如特别规则与工建通其他规则存在冲突，则以特别规则为准。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户在使用工建通提供的各项服务的同时，承诺接受并遵守各项相关规则的规定。工建通有权根据需要不时地制定、修改本协议或各类规则，如本协议有任何变</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">更，工建通将在网站上以公示形式通知予商户。如商户不同意相关变更，必须立即以书面通知的方式终止本协议。任何修订和新规则一经在工建通网公布即自动</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">生效，成为本协议的一部分。登录或继续使用服务将表示商户接受经修订的协议。除另行明确声明外，任何使服务范围扩大或功能增强的新内容均受本协议约束。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户签署或在线接受本协议并不导致本协议立即生效，经过工建通审核通过并向商户发出服务开通通知时，本协议即在商户和工建通之间产生法律效力。本协议不涉及商户与工建通网其它用户之间因网上交易而产生的法律关系及法律纠纷。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二．定义：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">“</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通</span><span 