mal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">四</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其发布于工建通的所有信息真实、准确，符合相关法律法规及工建通的规则。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">五</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其对其发布于工建通的交易信息中所涉商品有合法的销售权。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">六</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其将按照不低于《中华人民共和国消费者权益保护法》及其他法规、部门规章和国家强制性标准规定的要求，出售商品并提供相应的售后服务。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">七</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其明示只接受工建通提供的支付方式作为其通过工建通平台达成的交易的支付工具。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">八</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其保证在使用服务进行交易的过程中遵守诚实信用的原则，不在交易过程中采取不正当竞争行为，不扰乱网上交易的正常秩序，不从事与网上交易无关的行为。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">九</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其保证在使用服务时实施的所有行为均遵守国家法律、法规和工建通的相关规定以及各种社会公共利益或公共道德。如有违反导致任何法律后果的发生，商户将以自己的名义独立承担所有相应的法律责任；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其同意不对工建通平台上任何数据作商业性利用，包括但不限于在未经工建通事先书面批准的情况下，以复制、传播或向他方披露等方式使用在工建通平台上其他用户展示的任何资料；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其承诺拥有合法的权利和资格向工建通平台上传有关商品销售信息并进行销售，且前述行为未对任何第三方合法权益，包括但不限于第三方知识产权、物权等构成侵害，如因其行为导致工建通遭受任何第三方提起的索赔，诉讼或行政责任，其将承担相应责任并使工建通免责。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其任何其在线接受本协议并不当然导致本协议发生法律效力，本协议是附条件生效协议，即必须经过工建通对其提交的全部资料审核通过后方可生效。同时，</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其认可工建通有权独立的对其入驻资料、经营权限开通申请进行评估、判断。审核结果以工建通评估、判断为准，其对此不持有任何异议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其承诺不在发布的商品中使用任何未获授权品牌的关键字；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">四</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其承诺接受工建通平台对其出售商品是否具有合法进货来源的不定期检查，其有义务保留其商品具有合法进货来源的相关凭证。对于无法提供合法进货来源凭证的，工建通平台将根据实际情况对商品的真伪作出判断并根据本协议以及工建通平台相关规则进行处理，商户对此承担举证不利的后果。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十五</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其承诺接受工建通平台基于商品品质控制需求对其在售商品进行的质量抽检，其承诺对工建通选择的检测结果不持有异议。对于经检测证明存在质量瑕疵的商品，检测费用由商户承担。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十六</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如其在规定类目下经营商品的，则其承诺不单独销售其他类目商品。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">八、工建通的权利和义务：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">有义务在现有技术上维护整个应有卡网上交易平台的正常运行，并努力提升和改进技术，使商户网上交易活动得以顺利进行；工建通有权根据商户营业执照的经营范围以及商户对自己经营范围的描述自行决定</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">调整</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">允许商户发布商品的工建通商品类目种类和数量，商户对此不持任何异议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">对商户在注册使用服务中所遇到的与交易或注册有关的问题及反映的情况，工建通应及时作出回复；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">因网上交易平台的特殊性，工建通没有义务对所有商户的交易行为以及与交易有关的其它事项进行事先审查，但如存在下列情况：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">①第三方通知工建通，认为某个具体商户或具体交易事项可能存在重大问题；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">②商户或第三方向工建通告知交易平台上有违法或不当行为的；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通以普通非专业人员的知识水平标准对相关内容进行判别，可以认为这些内容或行为具有违法或不当性质的，工建通有权根据不同情况选择删除相关信息或停止对该商户提供服务，并追究相关法律责任。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">四</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通有权对商户的注册数据及交易行为进行查阅，发现注册数据或交易行为中存在任何问题或怀疑，均有权向商户发出询问或要求改正的通知，或者直接作出删除等处理；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">五</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">经国家生效法律文书或行政处罚决定确认商户存在违法行为，或者工建通有足够事实依据可以认定商户存在违法或违反协议行为的，工建通有权在工建通官方网站公布商户的违法和</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">/</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或违规行为；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">六</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">对于商户在工建通交易平台发布的下列各类信息，工建通有权在不通知商户的前提下进行删除或采取其它限制性措施，包括但不限于以规避费用为目的的信息；</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">以炒作信用为目的的信息；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通有理由相信存在欺诈等恶意或虚假内容的信息；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通有理由相信与网上交易无关或不是以交易为目的的信息；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通有理</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">由相信存在恶意竞价或其它试图扰乱正常交易秩序因素的信息；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通有理由相信属违反公共利益或可能严重损害工建通和</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">/</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或其它用户合法利益的信息；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">七</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户在此授予应有卡独家的、全球通用的、永久的、免费的许可使用权利</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> (</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">并有权对该权利进行再授权</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">，使工建通有权</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">全部或部份地</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">使用、复制、修订、改写、发布、翻译、分发、执行和展示商户公示于网站的各类信息或制作其派生作品，和</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">/</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或以现在已知或日后开发的任何形式、媒体或技术，</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">将上述信息纳入其它作品内；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">八</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通有权根据业务调整情况将本协议项下的全部权利义务一并转移给其关联公司，此种情况将会提前</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">7</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">天以网站公告的形式通知商户。商户承诺对此不持有异议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">九、费用规定：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户同意，就其使用的服务向工建通或工建通的关联公司</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">支付以下服务费用：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34