ht: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">服务期自服务实际开通日起算。工建通将按本协议规定的通知方式提前一天通知商户服务开通日。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如商户签署或在线接受本协议后三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(3)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">个工作日内仍未满足本条第一款规定的所有开通条件，或工建通因任何原因向商户发出拒绝提供服务的书面通知，则工建通有权不予开通服务，本协议即告终止。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(3