: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通在商户在线接受本协议，并经审查确认符合申请条件后，工建通可指令系统冻结其工建通账户内相应的金额作为保证金。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">保证金的管理和使用：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">除保证金的冻结外，工建通有权按以下方式就保证金的管理和使用发出指令：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如服务期内商户未有违反工建通各项规则的行为，且至停止使用服务后三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(3)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">个月内，商户未受到任何第三方投诉或发生交易纠纷，则工建通将在上述期限届满后的十</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(10)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">个工作日内解除对保证金的冻结，本协议另有规定的除外。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通可在以下情况发生时，处置保证金：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">在工建通网进行的交易中，如商户违反法律、法规、政策或违反其对买家的承诺致买家受损时，商户同意工建通有完全的权力根据应有卡的判断，直接使用保证金对买家进行赔付。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">在符合适用于工建通平台的相关消费者保障服务规则的情况下，如商户未在规则规定的时间内向买家履行相关义务，则工建通有权依其独立判断，直接使用保证金向买家退款。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如商户违反本协议和</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">/</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或工建通网站上的包括但不仅限于规则和流程、管理条例、规定等，给工建通造成任何损失</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">包括但不限于诉讼赔偿、诉讼费用、律师费用等</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">，或根据工建通的相关规则规定，工建通有权处罚违约罚金</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">罚金</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">，则工建通有权直接从保证金中扣除相当于工建通损失的金额或违约罚金</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">罚金</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">，保证金不足以赔偿的，工建通可继续向商户追偿。在损失金额不明确之前，工建通有权无限期要求继续冻结该保证金，直至损失金额明确后予以结算。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">．工建通如使用保证金对第三方进行任何赔付，应以书面方式</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">包括但不限于电子邮件、传真、</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">QQ</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">等</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">通知商户。在向商户出具的书面通知中，应说明赔付原因及赔付金额。赔付完成后，应向商户出具必要的赔付资金往来明细</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">以工建通账户资金明细为准</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">4</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">．</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">在本协议有效期内，商户应使保证金总额始终保持不低于根据第十条第</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">款规定的金额，如发生赔付事件导致保证金数额减少，则工建通有权继续冻结商户工建通账户中的余额以补足保证金；如余额不足，则商户应在赔付发生后三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(3)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">天内补足。保证金不足期间，工建通将部分或全部暂停向商户提供服务，如逾</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">期仍未能补足，则工建通有权终止本协议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">5</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">．如保证金不足赔付时，商户应自行支付额外的赔付金额，如因故导致工建通向买家支付了超出保证金数额的款项，或工建通因上述</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> ( 3 )</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">项列明的原因遭受的损失高于可支配的保证金余额，则工建通有权：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">要求商户偿付工建通的损失，且在指定时间内补足保证金；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">要求将商户工建通账户下的款项直接支付给应有卡，以补偿工建通所遭受的损失；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如工建通的损失通过上述二种方式仍无法弥补，则工建通有权单方面终止本协议。同时工建通保留通过法律途径向商户追偿的权利。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">6</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">．商户对买家、任何第三方以及工建通的赔付责任不以保证金的数额为限；除对商户保证金的处置外，工建通不对买家或者其他权利人承担任何其它赔付义务。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">7</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">．商户同意本条款所述保证金可以按照商户与工建通共同签订的《工建通平台入驻协议》约定之用途和程序使用。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十三、商户惩罚制度：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">出现超时赔付或者无货赔付订单时，会从押金中扣除</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">X</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">元</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">/</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">订单</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">每周赔付订单不得超过</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">10</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">笔，卖家被关闭出售资格后，剩余押金会如数退还</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">凡是触犯卖家违规条例中任何一条，停止销售</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">24</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">小时（酌情可对停止销售时间做增减处理）；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">卖家自行要求退出，即押金退还日起，</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">个月内不得再入驻；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">4.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通平台有权利对发布单价高于市场均价</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">10%</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">的商品进行强行撤销，，若商户不调整则不予以销售；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">5.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">交易过程中出现恶意辱骂客户现象，停止销售</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">48</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">小时；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">6.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">卖家需主动维护库存，出现负库存现象判定为卖家责任，停止销售</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">24</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">小时；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">7.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">卖家不得在工建通全站进行倒货买卖，一经发现取消入驻资格并永久不得入驻；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">8.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">不得出现分流引导现象</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">分单引导：主动引导买家去其他交易平台或者其他途径交易</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">，一经发现取消入驻资格并永久不得入驻；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">10.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如平台某款产品即将停止销售，管理将在产品停销前三天通知到相关卖家。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">11.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">未按订单要求发货的，视为发货不足；因卖家发货不足产生买卖家纠纷的，卖家必须在工建通客服人员要求卖家出具凭证之时起</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">10</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">分钟内提供凭证，</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">10</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">分钟内未提供判定为不足。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">12.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">卖家一周出现</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">次发货不足取消入驻资格。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">13.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">凡用户购买平台商品，</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">天内物品被官方</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">海关、警方等</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">没收，一经查证属实，均由卖家全额赔款。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十四、协议的终止：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">自然终止：如商户在线接受的工建通网站上的包括但不仅限于规则和流程、管理条例、规定因任何原因终止，则本协议将同时终止。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">通知解除：协议任何一方均可以提前十五</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(15)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">天书面通知的方式终止本协议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通单方解除权：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户违反工建通平台上的包括但不仅限于规则和流程、管理条例、规定等或本协议中的任何承诺或保证，包括但不限于本协议项下的任何约定，工建通都有权立刻终止本协议，且按有关规则对商户进行处罚。如或第三方多次投诉其商品质量或服务质量，则工建通除有权立即终止本协议外，还有权自商户工建通账户全额划扣其所有保证金，作为商户的违约金。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">四</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户在超过三十</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(30)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">天的时间内未以工建通平台服务账户及密码登录工建通平台的，工建通有权终止本协议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">五</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如非因工建通的原因，商户未能按本协议及附件之规定，按期全额支付有关服务费用和</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">/</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或活动费用，且在工建通规定的时限内仍未支付，工建通有权部分或全部中止或终止本协议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">六</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议规定的其他协议终止条件发生或实现，导致本协议终止。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">七</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">协议终止后有关事项的处理：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">协议终止后，工建通没有义务为商户保留工建通平台服务账户中或与之相关的任何信息，或转发任何未曾阅读或发送的信息给商户或第三方。亦不就终止协议而对商户或任何第三者承担任何责任；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">无论本协议因何原因终止，在协议终止前的行为所导致的任何赔偿和责任，商户必须完全且独立地承担；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3.</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">协议终止后，工建通有权保留该商户的注册数据及以前的交易行为记录。如商户在协议终止前在工建通交易平台上存在违法行为或违反协议的行为，工建通仍可行使本协议所规定的权利；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">4. </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">协议终止之前，</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户已经上传至工建通平台的商品信息尚未达成交易协议的，工建通有权在协议终止时同时删除此项商品的相关信息；</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户已经与另一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">用户就某商品信息达成交易协</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">议的，工建通可以不删除该项交易，但工建通有权在协议终止的同时将协议终止的的情况通知该交易中的买方。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">九</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如在协议期内，非因商户违约或过错导致本协议终止，则商户有权提交退款申请，要求工建通退还未履行部分的服务费用</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如有的话</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">至商户工建通账户。其他情况下协议发生终止，未履行服务费用均不予退还。其他费用在任何情况下都不予退回。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十五、协议期限：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议经商户在线接受且经过工建通审核通过后</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或书面签署后</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">即告生效，除非本协议规定的终止条件发生，本协议将持续有效。双方另有约定的除外。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十六、有效通知：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议下所规定的通知应以书面形式通过以下邮址递交收悉，通知的到达以应有卡收悉为准。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通：哈尔滨市道外区长江路</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1608</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">号华南城电子商务基地</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">B</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">馆</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">4</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">楼，邮编：</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">150090</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">收件人：工建通平台客户经理</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">收</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通可自邮址向商户在工建通平台提供的电子邮件地址发出通知。通知的送达以邮件发出为准。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十七、保密条款：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议所称商业秘密包括但不限于本协议、任何补充协议所述内容及在合作过程中涉及的其他秘密信息。任何一方未经商业秘密提供方同意，均不得将该信息向任何第三方披露、传播、编辑或展示。协议方承诺，本协议终止后仍承担此条款下的保密义务，保密期将另持续三年。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">因对方书面同意以及国家、行政、司法强制行为而披露商业秘密的，披露方不承担责任；该商业秘密已为公众所知悉的，披露方不承担责任。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十八、工建通的法律地位：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">平台仅作为用户物色交易对象，就物品和服务的交易进行协商，以及获取各类与交易相关的服务的信息。本协议的签署并不意味着工建通不对商户行为的合法性、有效性及商品的真实性、合法性和有效性作任何明示或暗示的担保。商户因进行交易、获取有偿服务或接触工建通平台服务器而发生的所有应纳税赋，均由商户自行负责支付。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">十九、有限责任：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">服务将按</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">&quot;</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">现状</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">&quot;</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">和按</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">&quot;</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">可得到</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">&quot;</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">的状态提供。工建通在此明确声明对服务不作任何明示或暗示的保证，包括但不限于对服务的可适用性，没有错误或疏漏，持续性，准确性，可靠性，适用于某一特定用途之类的保证，声明或承诺。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通对服务所涉的技术和信息的有效性，准确性，正确性，可靠性，质量，稳定，完整和及时性均不作承诺和保证。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">使用服务下载或者获取任何资料的行为均出于商户的独立判断并自行承担风险。每一个商户独自承担因此对其电脑系统或资料灭失造成的损失。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">不论在何种情况下，工建通均不对由于</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">Internet</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">连接故障，电脑，通讯或其他系统的故障，电力故障，罢工，劳动争议，暴乱，起义，骚乱，生产力或生</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">产资料不足，火灾，洪水，风暴，爆炸，不可抗力，战争，政府行为，国际、国内法院的命令或第三方的不作为而造成的不能服务或延迟服务承担责任。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">四</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">不论是否可以预见，不论是源于何种形式的行为，工建通不对由以下原因造成的任何特别的，直接的，间接的，惩罚性的，突发性的或有因果关系的损害或其他任何损害</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">包括但不限于利润或利息的损失，营业中断，资料灭失</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">承担责任。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">1. </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">使用或不能使用服务；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">2. </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">通过服务购买或获取任何商品，样品，数据，信息或进行交易等，或其他可替代上述行为的行为而产生的费用；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">3. </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">未经授权的存取或修改数据或数据的传输；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">4. </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">第三方通过服务所作的陈述或行为；</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">5. </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">其它与服务相关事件，包括疏忽等，所造成的损害。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二十、违约责任：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户同意赔偿由于使用服务</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">包括但不限于将商户资料展示在网站上</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">或违反本协议而给工建通造成的任何损失</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">包括由此产生的全额的诉讼费用和律师费</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">。商户同意工建通不对任何其张贴的资料，包括诽谤性的，攻击性的或非法的资料，承担任何责任；由于此类材料对其它用户造成的损失由商户自行全部承担。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">商户承诺，不会采取任何手段或措施，包括但不限于明示或暗示用户或通过其他方式转移其可以通过工建通平台在线达成的交易，或达成交易后不经由工建通帐号收取交易金额，以规避向工建通支付相关服务费用。否则将视为严重违约，工建通将有权立即终止本协议，并将其保证金作为违约金予以划扣，还可就违约行为向商户追偿。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">除本协议及工建通平台规则另有约定之外，如一方发生违约行为，守约方可以书面通知方式要求违约方在指定的时限内停止违约行为，并就违约行为造成的损失进行索赔，如违约方未能按时停止违约行为，则守约方有权立即终止本协议。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二十一、争议解决及其他：</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">一</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">本协议之解释与适用，以及与本协议有关的争议，均应依照中华人民共和国法律予以处理，并以哈尔滨市高级人民法院为第一审管辖法院。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">二</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">如本协议的任何条款被视作无效或无法执行，则上述条款可被分离，其余部份则仍具有法律效力。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); min-height: 21px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\"></span><br/></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">三</span><span style=\\\"font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\\\">)</span><span style=\\\"font-kerning: none\\\">工建通于商户过失或违约时放弃本协议规定的权利的，不得视为其对商户的其他或以后同类之过失或违约行为弃权。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '特讯科技', 1509496964, '', '0', '1', 'articles/17_11_01/59f918842211b.png', '', '工建通商户入驻协议', 0);
